<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-07-0319 </DOCNO><TEXT>Reviews and comments on the financial framework of the electricity supplyindustry. An account is given of the industry's financial performancewithin the terms of reference laid down for it by the government. Ananalysis of customer service performance is also given, although theauthors note their dissatisfaction with the existing information frameworkavailable for judging this. Their ideas on improving industry accountabilityto consumers are included and relevant tables from the Electricity Council'sPerformance Indicators 1986/87 are given. The accountancy method usedthroughout is Current Cost Accounting (CCA).</TEXT></DOC>